{
  "stem": "377.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were not hungry at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Until, until-- we were in Schindler's-- until the order came to go to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were in Schindler's then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then in Brunnlitz was a different story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were-- we, we worked, we were supposed to work in the-- I don't know what they had it for, to the, to the, to the planes, or to the trains, or to the-- I don't know, anything.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they said, he said, he brainwashed them that its so and so many go out daily.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so and so many go out this way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he brain-- I don't know how he, how did, but-- and he took in very many Jews next to the, to the other part, what he built over there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this is how, how, how it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we didn't know that the war is over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't know that there was coming over, coming to be over in few days or so.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we only, we only heard about something that he took few, few men out from there, and he, and he dressed them up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took a, they took something to open up a train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know the trains what came?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not the train what you sit there, only-- Transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cattle car.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't know what for.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All of a sudden, we saw a bunch of people coming all frozen, all hungry, frozen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they looked like, like they will, they will, they will not live.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they went to another barrack over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they lived!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They lived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were-- they lived until we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then, I didn't know what might happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I asked Page what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Page told me that they live.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
